---
// The dedicated manual-create page is consolidated into the /generate toggle
// surface (R4). Preserve any existing bookmarks/links by redirecting straight
// into the Manual mode of that surface.
//
// We set the redirect via Astro.response rather than `return Astro.redirect()`:
// a bare top-level `return` in a body-less frontmatter crashes
// @typescript-eslint's no-misused-promises rule (it can't resolve the return's
// enclosing function). This form is equivalent and lints cleanly.
Astro.response.status = 302;
Astro.response.headers.set("Location", "/generate?mode=manual");
---
